<i>Though the target</i>
<i>on their back</i>

01:28.963 --> 01:31.424
<i>only adds to the pressure</i>
<i>of the occasion.</i>

01:31.466 --> 01:33.593
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

01:33.635 --> 01:35.387
<i>After all, they play a game</i>

01:35.428 --> 01:38.306
<i>that has a habit</i>
<i>of laughing at expectations</i>

01:38.348 --> 01:40.225
<i>with no place for sentiment.</i>

01:40.266 --> 01:41.559
Push.

01:41.601 --> 01:43.395
<i>- Because the perfect</i>
<i>sheet of ice</i>

