<i>is the ultimate</i>
<i>level playing field...</i>

01:46.648 --> 01:47.899
Hard!

01:47.941 --> 01:49.442
<i>Where you never know</i>

01:49.484 --> 01:52.821
<i>where the story</i>
<i>will slide next.</i>

