02:49.669 --> 02:50.837
kinda therapeutic honestly

02:50.879 --> 02:52.881
in the middle
of this kinda stuff.

02:53.631 --> 02:56.801
<i>- I finally feel like</i>
<i>I'm excited to be here.</i>

